All Implemented Interfaces:
CoAPConstants, coap.RequestHandler
public abstract class AbstractJavaScriptResource
extends JavaScriptResource

If an object in JavaScript (Rhino) is of type AbstractJavaScriptResource, it is possible to add further methods and fields in JavaScript. However, in this case it is not possible to use any other than the empty constructor. If the consturctor Resource(String) is required, use JavaScriptResource.

Martin Lanter
